reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 23, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great brushes for cleaning
reviews.reviewText: I like to review every product I buy on Amazon, mainly because others can then make their own purchases based on what the reviews say. I buy like that, and hope others do too. In this case, I am almost embarrassed to post this review, because these were purchased to clean, but not teeth. I use this particular toothbrush to clean jewelry and other small parts that I have in my home and office. I'm not sure Colgate will appreciate me saying this, but these work great with Murphy's oil soap and silver polish.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great, cheap, toothbrushes!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for a trip my family took. They’re awesome because they’re cheap and I can stuff them into a ziplock and call it a day.
